{"id": 707, "genre": 1001, "title": "今年你最后悔的一笔消费是什么？", "description": "世事变幻，单纯的我措手不及。（题图来自：KELSEY DAKE）", "record_count": 6173, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194340aofyJjcV1Zx9NPQs.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-12-18T12:09:22Z", "options": [{"id": 45312, "content": "买了一双鞋，小了，然而没换！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 404706}, {"id": 35841, "content": "青春", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 374731}, {"id": 35075, "content": "11.11", "image": null, "praise_count": 276, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 285511}, {"id": 35076, "content": "忘了在双十一买东西，结果只能在12号，13号买。", "image": null, "praise_count": 132, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197974}, {"id": 35077, "content": "在网站上买化妆品，总感觉是假的", "image": null, "praise_count": 148, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 350599}, {"id": 38405, "content": "呵呵哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 399710}, {"id": 35078, "content": "脑子一热买了某粗粮的路由器现在频繁掉包谁来救救我", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 68844}, {"id": 35079, "content": "买车库和车", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321016}, {"id": 41479, "content": "买了果s 不出俩礼拜 cèi 了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416583}, {"id": 35080, "content": "买了音乐网站的会员结果因为版权问题歌曲不断下架", "image": null, "praise_count": 444, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 68844}, {"id": 35081, "content": "感觉没有啥大宗消费可是就是没存到钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 676, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252804}, {"id": 35593, "content": "每次淘宝东西发来后都是后悔的?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 372530}, {"id": 35082, "content": "点都德", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 168505}, {"id": 35594, "content": "在台湾买了几件据说是潮牌的衣服，回来大家都说不适合我。看祖马龙香水，柜台说买够1200减100，然后冲动消费了两瓶各100毫升的香水，不知何年何月喷完。买日本产的保温杯，还买了5个，结果家里人看不上说太丑，只好在家积灰。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 364174}, {"id": 39434, "content": "堕胎", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 400873}, {"id": 35083, "content": "今年气温变化忒大，那么冷，结果狠下心双十一订了一床有点小贵的厚被子，等到货的时候，家里暖气又很足，盖不住的节奏……", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 323781}, {"id": 35595, "content": "在台湾买祖马龙香水，柜台说买够1200减100，冲动买了两瓶各100毫升的，不知何年何月喷完。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 364174}, {"id": 36875, "content": "E租宝", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340064}, {"id": 35084, "content": "最后悔没买什么，也没钱了", "image": null, "praise_count": 589, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 91804}, {"id": 35852, "content": "被路边的传单哥带到美容院……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 280117}, {"id": 35085, "content": "被甩之前帮前女友买东西花光了所有的积蓄???", "image": null, "praise_count": 380, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 330163}, {"id": 35086, "content": "说说去年 买辆山地 逛完超市出来就没了", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246331}, {"id": 35087, "content": "被损友忽悠买发烧级耳机，却没时间用，用的次数不超过十次", "image": null, "praise_count": 66, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265394}, {"id": 35343, "content": "和女友开房钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 323180}, {"id": 36623, "content": "头上长草的薰衣草", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 380275}, {"id": 35088, "content": "想用la mer面霜换PS4", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181495}, {"id": 35600, "content": "虎牌保温杯大减价，一口气买了5个，还买了贵一倍的日本产。结果家人嫌太丑不要还笑话我。只好把把杯子搁家里积灰。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 364174}, {"id": 35089, "content": "炉石搞了一 套全金机械法就不玩了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 366516}, {"id": 35602, "content": "把一个可以帮我买单的男票甩了 ：）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 372132}, {"id": 35091, "content": "年初说了要破处，可是那次去女朋友家睡的是沙发。", "image": null, "praise_count": 144, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 357132}, {"id": 35347, "content": "跟风买了kanye穿的很多东西 最后发现椰子不过如此 BV的切尔西也没有出彩的方面 花了这么多钱 不如陪陪父母到全国各地看看 后悔 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 268067}, {"id": 35092, "content": "京东秒杀的一枝春洗面奶，还以为是欧莱雅。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219307}, {"id": 35093, "content": "办了百度云盘会员，，，结果全和谐了", "image": null, "praise_count": 181, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 366781}, {"id": 35349, "content": "下午6级，这个报名费亏了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 370189}, {"id": 36885, "content": "消费了马上就后悔", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 385865}, {"id": 38933, "content": "kindle paper3", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403739}, {"id": 35094, "content": "去某某成人国际培训机构 都不知道学了啥 反正钱没少花 还啥啥都贵", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 367504}, {"id": 35606, "content": "买了一台psv2000，游戏好贵啊而且画质不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 372575}, {"id": 36374, "content": "最后悔买了便宜的橱柜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 380303}, {"id": 35095, "content": "买一堆没用的", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115714}, {"id": 35607, "content": "哎，我买了一个iphone当时5000多，现在只卖2000多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 352669}, {"id": 35096, "content": "英语四六级&计算机二级&考研报名费", "image": null, "praise_count": 373, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 342174}, {"id": 35097, "content": "目前排名前六的我占全了", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335491}, {"id": 35098, "content": "不自量力报名雅思然后弃考", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235507}, {"id": 35354, "content": "海淘一双鞋，小了；海淘牛仔裤，大了；屁股坐电脑上，坏了......", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 370230}, {"id": 46106, "content": "总觉得手机会坏，买了备用机。结果备用机坏了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 453074}, {"id": 35355, "content": "海淘买了个明知不适合自己却yy能适合自己的包 现在连老爸都不待见它", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 261003}, {"id": 35611, "content": "买了台电脑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 345898}, {"id": 40219, "content": "冲了黄钻", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 415859}, {"id": 35101, "content": "英语四六级 计算机二级 考研?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 342174}]}